'Our Departments'),(546,19,'_content_block_with_cta_heading','field_5acc74966352a'),(547,19,'content_block_with_cta_paragraph_1','Running the UK is complicated. That\'s why the Civil Service is divided into departments, which deal with areas such as education, health and defence – all the issues which the government needs to run the country. A lot of departments will have their own agencies dealing with specialist subjects.'),(548,19,'_content_block_with_cta_paragraph_1','field_5acc74a56352b'),(549,19,'content_block_with_cta_paragraph_2','Whatever your passion – from the environment to health, there\'s a department or agency to match.'),(550,19,'_content_block_with_cta_paragraph_2','field_5acc77a7d984a'),(551,19,'content_block_with_cta_cta_text','Discover our departments'),(552,19,'_content_block_with_cta_cta_text','field_5acc74bf6352c'),(553,19,'content_block_with_cta_cta_target','https://CAREERS-SITE.URL/departments/'),(554,19,'_content_block_with_cta_cta_target','field_5acc74e66352d'),(555,19,'content_block_with_cta',''),(556,19,'_content_block_with_cta','field_5acc747a63529'),(557,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_heading','Our Professions'),(558,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_heading','field_5acc79c9bc6eb'),(559,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_paragraph_1','Every Civil Service job is also part of a \'profession\' – everything from legal and IT to HR or serice delivery.'),(560,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_paragraph_1','field_5acc79ddbc6ec'),(561,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_paragraph_2','Your profession offers networking opportunities and training and development programmes – plus the chance to work on major cross-government projects.'),(562,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_paragraph_2','field_5acc79f8bc6ed'),(563,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_cta_text','Discover our professions'),(564,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_cta_text','field_5acc7a258fa7f'),(565,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_cta_target','https://CAREERS-SITE.URL/our-community/'),(566,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_cta_target','field_5acc7a348fa80'),(567,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image_image','12'),(568,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image_image','field_5acc7a5e962b8'),(569,19,'content_block_with_cta_+_image',''),(570,19,'_content_block_with_cta_+_image','field_5acc79aabc6ea'),(571,19,'content_block_image_heading','Where you\'ll find us'),(572,19,'_content_block_image_heading','field_5acc9520ce57a'),(573,19,'content_block_image_body','We\'re everywhere. You\'ll find locations right across the UK – a far cry from the cliché of the  bowler-hatted Westminster civil servant. In fact, just 18% of our jobs are based in London.'),(574,19,'_content_block_image_body','field_5acc9537ce57b'),(575,19,'content_block_image_image','6'),(576,19,'_content_block_image_image','field_5acc956e20072'),(577,19,'content_block_image',''),(578,19,'_content_block_image','field_5acc9513ce579'),(579,19,'content_block_promo_promo_tag','Latest'),(580,19,'_content_block_promo_promo_tag','field_5acc818918f13'),(581,19,'content_block_promo_heading','Bringing digital tranformation to culture: be part of the revolution'),(582,19,'_content_block_promo_heading','field_5acc7e8a3622d'),(583,19,'content_block_promo_heading_target','https://www.gov.uk/'),(584,19,'_content_block_promo_heading_target','field_5acc7e9d3622e'),(585,19,'content_block_promo_paragraph_1','The way people consume arts and culture is changing: learn how the Department for Digital, Culture, Media & Sport (DCMS) is changing to meet this challenge, and the talent we\'re looking for – right now.'),(586,19,'_content_block_promo_paragraph_1','field_5acc7f1126bac'),(587,19,'content_block_promo_cta_text_before','Find out more about '),(588,19,'_content_block_promo_cta_text_before','field_5acc836345f14'),(589,19,'content_block_promo_cta_target_text','working for DCMS'),(590,19,'_content_block_promo_cta_target_text','field_5acc83f651f8e'),(591,19,'content_block_promo_cta_target_link','https://www.gov.uk/'),(592,19,'_content_block_promo_cta_target_link','field_5acc841551f8f'),(593,19,'content_block_promo_cta_text_after','.'),(594,19,'_content_block_promo_cta_text_after','field_5acc838945f15'),(595,19,'content_block_promo_cta',''),(596,19,'_content_block_promo_cta','field_5acc835145f13'),(597,19,'content_block_promo_image','12'),(598,19,'_content_block_promo_image','field_5acc7f6db9a87'),(599,19,'content_block_promo',''),(600,19,'_content_block_promo','field_5acc7e673622c'),(601,13,'rpg-team','13'),(602,20,'_edit_last','1'),(603,20,'_edit_lock','1525358943:1'),(604,20,'_wp_page_template','default'),(605,20,'billboard_logo_text','HMRC'),(606,20,'_billboard_logo_text','field_5ac4d0a0f95d7'),(607,20,'billboard_logo','8'),(608,20,'_billboard_logo','field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(609,20,'billboard_heading','Working for HMRC'),(610,20,'_billboard_heading','field_5ac4d11ed8315'),(611,20,'billboard_intro_text','Tax is a fact of life, and it\'s what keeps the UK running. We calculate and collect all the taxes, duties and VAT that people and companies pay. We help keep our borders safe, make sure that the lowest paid have the protection of the national minimum wage, and that polluters pay their fair share of  environmental taxes.'),(612,20,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5accbb890d0c3'),(613,20,'billboard_image','12'),(614,20,'_billboard_image','field_5accbbcfbcd0d'),(615,20,'billboard',''),(616,20,'_billboard','field_5ac4d08bf95d6'),(617,20,'main_content_heading','Trust, respect and openness'),(618,20,'_main_content_heading','field_5ac4d5e562da0'),(619,20,'main_content_paragraph_1','But it\'s not just what we do – it\'s how we do it. We don\'t expect anyone to enjoy paying tax, but we do want them to feel confident that we treat everyone fairly. That means being clear, fair and straightforward with taxpayers, and sorting any mistakes as quickly as possible. And realising that for many people, like those who rely on tax credits, we can change people\'s lives.'),(620,20,'_main_content_paragraph_1','field_5ac4d60162da1'),(621,20,'main_content_paragraph_2','Whatever your role at HMRC, you\'ll be amongst people with an incredible range of skills and experience. Our diverse teams help us do better work, as they truly reflect the people we\'re working for - the great British public. Plus, it\'s the right thing to do.'),(622,20,'_main_content_paragraph_2','field_5ac4d65cd4870'),(623,20,'main_content_image_1','12'),(624,20,'_main_content_image_1','field_5ac4d6e6993f0'),(625,20,'main_content_paragraph_3','Almost everyone comes into contact with us at some point – like it or not this makes customer service central to everything we do. In fact, our work is as much about people as it is about money. If you\'re working in a customer-facing role, you\'ll need to balance tact, empathy and a thick skin.'),(626,20,'_main_content_paragraph_3','field_5ac4d66bd4871'),(627,20,'main_content_image_2','12'),(628,20,'_main_content_image_2','field_5ac4d6f8993f1'),(629,20,'main_content_paragraph_4',''),(630,20,'_main_content_paragraph_4','field_5ad0898470360'),(631,20,'main_content',''),(632,20,'_main_content','field_5ac4d5c762d9f'),(633,20,'content_block_vertical_image','12'),(634,20,'_content_block_vertical_image','field_5ac4d76b70507'),(635,20,'content_block_vertical_quote','Diverse teams deliver better, and more creative results. But I also believe that the experience of working in diverse work environments has helped shape me as an individual and a professional.'),(636,20,'_content_block_vertical_quote','field_5ac4d77670508'),(637,20,'content_block_vertical_forename','Hardik'),(638,20,'_content_block_vertical_forename','field_5ac4d7d894b09'),(639,20,'content_block_vertical_surname','Shah'),(640,20,'_content_block_vertical_surname','field_5ac4d7ea94b0a'),(641,20,'content_block_vertical_role','Deputy Director, HMRC'),(642,20,'_content_block_vertical_role','field_5ac4d7f794b0b'),(643,20,'content_block_vertical',''),(644,20,'_content_block_vertical','field_5ac4d74770506'),(645,20,'factoid_factoid_0_fact','Last year, we collected half a trillion pounds. That\'s right: half a trillion.'),(646,20,'_factoid_factoid_0_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(647,20,'factoid_factoid_1_fact','We employ over 56,000 people.'),(648,20,'_factoid_factoid_1_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(649,20,'factoid_factoid_2_fact','We have great lawyers: we win around 80% of the tax avoidance cases that go to court.'),(650,20,'_factoid_factoid_2_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(651,20,'factoid_factoid','3'),(652,20,'_factoid_factoid','field_5ac4d8e5debdb'),(653,20,'factoid',''),(654,20,'_factoid','field_5ac4d8cbd4cf0'),(655,20,'content_block_horizontal_image','12'),(656,20,'_content_block_horizontal_image','field_5ac6064cd5934'),(657,20,'content_block_horizontal_quote','Being an HMRC apprentice means I get to work with lots of really skilled people and to soak up knowledge and learn from them.'),(658,20,'_content_block_horizontal_quote','field_5ac60663d5935'),(659,20,'content_block_horizontal_forename','Joe'),(660,20,'_content_block_horizontal_forename','field_5ac6069bd5936'),(661,20,'content_block_horizontal_surname','Powell'),(662,20,'_content_block_horizontal_surname','field_5ac606b1d5937'),(663,20,'content_block_horizontal_role','HMRC Digital Delivery Centres'),(664,20,'_content_block_horizontal_role','field_5ac606c3d5938'),(665,20,'content_block_horizontal_extra_text','We\'ll give you the opportunity to use your skills to build a rewarding career. From the moment you join, we\'ll help you identify your goals and tap into the huge variety of training we offer. Last year, X,000 of our people trained or gained qualifications with us. And if you want to broaden your experience even further, you\'ll be able to work outside your department on major cross-government projects.'),(666,20,'_content_block_horizontal_extra_text','field_5ac606d7d5939'),(667,20,'content_block_horizontal',''),(668,20,'_content_block_horizontal','field_5ac60605d5933'),(669,20,'sub_content_heading','Where we\'re heading'),(670,20,'_sub_content_heading','field_5ac6182a357b6'),(671,20,'sub_content_intro','We have one of the biggest and most dynamic IT operations in Europe, and by 2020 we will be among the most digitally advanced tax authorities in the world. To get there, we want to hire passionate and creative digital specialists.'),(672,20,'_sub_content_intro','field_5ac61855357b7'),(673,20,'sub_content_driver_0_image','12'),(674,20,'_sub_content_driver_0_image','field_5ac61941a49dc'),(675,20,'sub_content_driver_0_headline','Winning the battle against tax avoidance'),(676,20,'_sub_content_driver_0_headline','field_5ac6195fa49dd'),(677,20,'sub_content_driver_0_link','https://www.gov.uk/'),(678,20,'_sub_content_driver_0_link','field_5ac61ca4cd4b8'),(679,20,'sub_content_driver_0_text','Our specialist teams are taking on the global tax-avoidance industry - and winning.'),(680,20,'_sub_content_driver_0_text','field_5ac61970a49de'),(681,20,'sub_content_driver_1_image','12'),(682,20,'_sub_content_driver_1_image','field_5ac61941a49dc'),(683,20,'sub_content_driver_1_headline','Winning the battle against tax avoidance'),(684,20,'_sub_content_driver_1_headline','field_5ac6195fa49dd'),(685,20,'sub_content_driver_1_link','https://www.gov.uk/'),(686,20,'_sub_content_driver_1_link','field_5ac61ca4cd4b8'),(687,20,'sub_content_driver_1_text','Winning the battle against tax avoidance'),(688,20,'_sub_content_driver_1_text','field_5ac61970a49de'),(689,20,'sub_content_driver','2'),(690,20,'_sub_content_driver','field_5ac6190fa49db'),(691,20,'sub_content',''),(692,20,'_sub_content','field_5ac6180c357b5'),(693,21,'billboard_logo_text',''),(694,21,'_billboard_logo_text','field_5ac4d0a0f95d7'),(695,21,'billboard_logo',''),(696,21,'_billboard_logo','field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(697,21,'billboard_heading',''),(698,21,'_billboard_heading','field_5ac4d11ed8315'),(699,21,'billboard_intro_text',''),(700,21,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5accbb890d0c3'),(701,21,'billboard_image',''),(702,21,'