22,'_sub_content','field_5ac6180c357b5'),(871,23,'billboard_logo_text','HMRC'),(872,23,'_billboard_logo_text','field_5ac4d0a0f95d7'),(873,23,'billboard_logo','8'),(874,23,'_billboard_logo','field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(875,23,'billboard_heading','Working for HMRC'),(876,23,'_billboard_heading','field_5ac4d11ed8315'),(877,23,'billboard_intro_text','Tax is a fact of life, and it\'s what keeps the UK running. We calculate and collect all the taxes, duties and VAT that people and companies pay. We help keep our borders safe, make sure that the lowest paid have the protection of the national minimum wage, and that polluters pay their fair share of  environmental taxes.'),(878,23,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5accbb890d0c3'),(879,23,'billboard_image','12'),(880,23,'_billboard_image','field_5accbbcfbcd0d'),(881,23,'billboard',''),(882,23,'_billboard','field_5ac4d08bf95d6'),(883,23,'main_content_heading','Trust, respect and openness'),(884,23,'_main_content_heading','field_5ac4d5e562da0'),(885,23,'main_content_paragraph_1','But it\'s not just what we do – it\'s how we do it. We don\'t expect anyone to enjoy paying tax, but we do want them to feel confident that we treat everyone fairly. That means being clear, fair and straightforward with taxpayers, and sorting any mistakes as quickly as possible. And realising that for many people, like those who rely on tax credits, we can change people\'s lives.'),(886,23,'_main_content_paragraph_1','field_5ac4d60162da1'),(887,23,'main_content_paragraph_2','Whatever your role at HMRC, you\'ll be amongst people with an incredible range of skills and experience. Our diverse teams help us do better work, as they truly reflect the people we\'re working for - the great British public. Plus, it\'s the right thing to do.'),(888,23,'_main_content_paragraph_2','field_5ac4d65cd4870'),(889,23,'main_content_image_1','12'),(890,23,'_main_content_image_1','field_5ac4d6e6993f0'),(891,23,'main_content_paragraph_3','Almost everyone comes into contact with us at some point – like it or not this makes customer service central to everything we do. In fact, our work is as much about people as it is about money. If you\'re working in a customer-facing role, you\'ll need to balance tact, empathy and a thick skin.'),(892,23,'_main_content_paragraph_3','field_5ac4d66bd4871'),(893,23,'main_content_image_2','12'),(894,23,'_main_content_image_2','field_5ac4d6f8993f1'),(895,23,'main_content_paragraph_4',''),(896,23,'_main_content_paragraph_4','field_5ad0898470360'),(897,23,'main_content',''),(898,23,'_main_content','field_5ac4d5c762d9f'),(899,23,'content_block_vertical_image','12'),(900,23,'_content_block_vertical_image','field_5ac4d76b70507'),(901,23,'content_block_vertical_quote','Diverse teams deliver better, and more creative results. But I also believe that the experience of working in diverse work environments has helped shape me as an individual and a professional.'),(902,23,'_content_block_vertical_quote','field_5ac4d77670508'),(903,23,'content_block_vertical_forename','Hardik'),(904,23,'_content_block_vertical_forename','field_5ac4d7d894b09'),(905,23,'content_block_vertical_surname','Shah'),(906,23,'_content_block_vertical_surname','field_5ac4d7ea94b0a'),(907,23,'content_block_vertical_role','Deputy Director, HMRC'),(908,23,'_content_block_vertical_role','field_5ac4d7f794b0b'),(909,23,'content_block_vertical',''),(910,23,'_content_block_vertical','field_5ac4d74770506'),(911,23,'factoid_factoid_0_fact',''),(912,23,'_factoid_factoid_0_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(913,23,'factoid_factoid_1_fact',''),(914,23,'_factoid_factoid_1_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(915,23,'factoid_factoid_2_fact',''),(916,23,'_factoid_factoid_2_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(917,23,'factoid_factoid','3'),(918,23,'_factoid_factoid','field_5ac4d8e5debdb'),(919,23,'factoid',''),(920,23,'_factoid','field_5ac4d8cbd4cf0'),(921,23,'content_block_horizontal_image',''),(922,23,'_content_block_horizontal_image','field_5ac6064cd5934'),(923,23,'content_block_hor