field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(1388,28,'billboard_heading','Working in project management and delivery'),(1389,28,'_billboard_heading','field_5acb7982f284a'),(1390,28,'billboard_intro_text','Government is in the middle of huge, transformational projects, with more on the horizon. The profile and prestige of project delivery professionals in the public sector has never been higher.'),(1391,28,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5acb79ea29832'),(1392,28,'billboard_image','9'),(1393,28,'_billboard_image','field_5acb79be29831'),(1394,28,'billboard',''),(1395,28,'_billboard','field_5acb795af2849'),(1396,28,'main_content_heading','Making change happen'),(1397,28,'_main_content_heading','field_5ac4d5e562da0'),(1398,28,'main_content_paragraph_1','Project delivery in the Civil Service is about transforming society. Our projects help improve people\'s lives and make government work better. '),(1399,28,'_main_content_paragraph_1','field_5ac4d60162da1'),(1400,28,'main_content_paragraph_2','Our projects are complex, ambitious and huge - really huge. We\'re currently spending around £500 billion on things like, making Tax Digital - the whole system, end-to end, creating an online court system and a digital census ready for 2021.\r\nMake no mistake, when we say you\'ll have the chance to change the UK for the better, we mean it.'),(1401,28,'_main_content_paragraph_2','field_5ac4d65cd4870'),(1402,28,'main_content_image_1','12'),(1403,28,'_main_content_image_1','field_5ac4d6e6993f0'),(1404,28,'main_content_paragraph_3','The Project Delivery profession is there to embed this vital skill, and support everyone involved in planning, supporting and delivering projects. We\'re fairly new, but growing fast. When you join us, you\'ll become part of a thriving community, with networks promoting collaboration, sharing best practices, offering advice and support, and informing strategies.'),(1405,28,'_main_content_paragraph_3','field_5ac4d66bd4871'),(1406,28,'main_content_image_2','12'),(1407,28,'_main_content_image_2','field_5ac4d6f8993f1'),(1408,28,'main_content_paragraph_4','We\'ll help you plan your career path, with guidance and formal mentoring available from colleagues who\'ve seen - and done - it all.\r\nWe offer a dedicated project delivery curriculum which blends work-based, online and classroom learning in line with best practice from top performing public and private sector organisations. And many of our courses come with accredited or validated qualifications.'),(1409,28,'_main_content_paragraph_4','field_5ad0898470360'),(1410,28,'main_content',''),(1411,28,'_main_content','field_5ac4d5c762d9f'),(1412,28,'content_block_vertical_image','12'),(1413,28,'_content_block_vertical_image','field_5ac4d76b70507'),(1414,28,'content_block_vertical_quote','I\'m working on some of the country\'s most pressing security projects on a scale unparalleled in the private sector.'),(1415,28,'_content_block_vertical_quote','field_5ac4d77670508'),(1416,28,'content_block_vertical_forename','Gregg'),(1417,28,'_content_block_vertical_forename','field_5ac4d7d894b09'),(1418,28,'content_block_vertical_surname','Harfleet'),(1419,28,'_content_block_vertical_surname','field_5ac4d7ea94b0a'),(1420,28,'content_block_vertical_role','Civil Service Fast Stream, Ministry of Defence'),(1421,28,'_content_block_vertical_role','field_5ac4d7f794b0b'),(1422,28,'content_block_vertical',''),(1423,28,'_content_block_vertical','field_5ac4d74770506'),(1424,28,'factoid_factoid_0_fact',''),(1425,28,'_factoid_factoid_0_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(1426,28,'factoid_factoid_1_fact',''),(1427,28,'_factoid_factoid_1_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(1428,28,'factoid_factoid_2_fact',''),(1429,28,'_factoid_factoid_2_fact','field_5ac4da06bad8f'),(1430,28,'factoid_factoid','3'),(1431,28,'_factoid_factoid','field_5ac4d8e5debdb'),(1432,28,'factoid',''),(1433,28,'_factoid','field_5ac4d8cbd4cf0'),(1434,28,'content_block_horizontal_image',''),(1435,28,'_content_block_horizontal_image','field_5ac6064cd5934'),(1436,28,'cont