er','2'),(1557,29,'_sub_content_driver','field_5ac6190fa49db'),(1558,29,'sub_content',''),(1559,29,'_sub_content','field_5ac6180c357b5'),(1561,28,'_edit_lock','1525359462:1'),(1562,28,'sub_repeater_items_0_heading','10,000-strong… and growing fast'),(1563,28,'_sub_repeater_items_0_heading','field_5acdc4b3f678b'),(1564,28,'sub_repeater_items_0_heading_target','https://www.gov.uk/'),(1565,28,'_sub_repeater_items_0_heading_target','field_5acdc4c6f678c'),(1566,28,'sub_repeater_items_0_body','Charlotte Radford tells us about current and future plans to strengthen the government\'s Project Delivery Profession.'),(1567,28,'_sub_repeater_items_0_body','field_5acdc4d6f678d'),(1568,28,'sub_repeater_items_0_image','12'),(1569,28,'_sub_repeater_items_0_image','field_5acdc4f3f678e'),(1570,28,'sub_repeater_items_1_heading','Professionalising the delivery of change'),(1571,28,'_sub_repeater_items_1_heading','field_5acdc4b3f678b'),(1572,28,'sub_repeater_items_1_heading_target','https://www.gov.uk/'),(1573,28,'_sub_repeater_items_1_heading_target','field_5acdc4c6f678c'),(1574,28,'sub_repeater_items_1_body','Steve Vine, head of the Project Delivery Profession at the Ministry of Justice, believes project professionals who know how to deliver change have a big role to play in transforming government.'),(1575,28,'_sub_repeater_items_1_body','field_5acdc4d6f678d'),(1576,28,'sub_repeater_items_1_image','12'),(1577,28,'_sub_repeater_items_1_image','field_5acdc4f3f678e'),(1578,28,'sub_repeater_items_2_heading','5 top tips for successful project delivery'),(1579,28,'_sub_repeater_items_2_heading','field_5acdc4b3f678b'),(1580,28,'sub_repeater_items_2_heading_target','https://www.gov.uk/'),(1581,28,'_sub_repeater_items_2_heading_target','field_5acdc4c6f678c'),(1582,28,'sub_repeater_items_2_body','Suzanne Newton has just completed a project which successfully moved 41 million employees to the real-time PAYE system: discover what she learned from the process.'),(1583,28,'_sub_repeater_items_2_body','field_5acdc4d6f678d'),(1584,28,'sub_repeater_items_2_image','12'),(1585,28,'_sub_repeater_items_2_image','field_5acdc4f3f678e'),(1586,28,'sub_repeater_items','3'),(1587,28,'_sub_repeater_items','field_5acdc49ef678a'),(1588,28,'sub_repeater',''),(1589,28,'_sub_repeater','field_5acdc481f6789'),(1590,28,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','Make a real difference'),(1591,28,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','field_5ad09fb6a4e80'),(1592,28,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','You\'ll be based in a particular department, but don\'t expect to be there forever. You\'ll be part of a talent pool – called upon to work wherever you can add value.'),(1593,28,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','field_5ad09fd4a4e81'),(1594,28,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','You\'ll also get the chance to work on our cross-department Smarter Working Programmes. They may not sound glamorous, but it\'s how we\'re transforming the entire Civil Service.'),(1595,28,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','field_5ad09ff8a4e82'),(1596,28,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','Big enough for you?'),(1597,28,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','field_5ad0a185f893c'),(1598,28,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras',''),(1599,28,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras','field_5ad0a61054bc4_field_5ad09f94a4e7f'),(1600,28,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','Discipline, flexibility and creativity'),(1601,28,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','field_5ad09fb6a4e80'),(1602,28,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','Whatever your level or experience, you\'ll neeed to have the passion and drive to support the delivery of projects at scale. You’ll need to be adaptable - goals, timescales and even the political environment can change, and you\'ll need the skills and creativity to adapt. '),(1603,28,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','field_5ad09fd4a4e81'),(1604,28,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','And beyond your formal skills, you\'ll need to be brilliant at building relationships - with the huge range of people who\'ll make your project a success.'),(1605,28,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','field_5ad09ff8a4e82'),(1606,28,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','We\'re Agile, but we\'re flexible and imaginative in how we work : we\'ll expect you to adapt the delivery methodologies to each unique situation. '),(1607,28,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','field_5ad0a185f893c'),(1608,28,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras',''),(1609,28,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras','field_5ad0a61054bc4_field_5ad09f94a4e7f'),(1610,28,'sub_content_multiple','2'),(1611,28,'_sub_content_multiple','field_5ad0a5dc54bc3'),(1612,28,'listing_heading','We\'re looking for specialists in:'),(1613,28,'_listing_heading','field_5ad0b7bcf2edb'),(1614,28,'listing_items_0_item','Project Delivery'),(1615,28,'_listing_items_0_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1616,28,'listing_items_1_item','Project Management'),(1617,28,'_listing_items_1_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1618,28,'listing_items_2_item','Business Case, Budget and Resources'),(1619,28,'_listing_items_2_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1620,28,'listing_items_3_item','Stakeholder Management'),(1621,28,'_listing_items_3_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1622,28,'listing_items_4_item','Risk Management'),(1623,28,'_listing_items_4_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1624,28,'listing_items_5_item','Project Performance, Controls and Assurance'),(1625,28,'_listing_items_5_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1626,28,'listing_items','6'),(1627,28,'_listing_items','field_5ad0b7ccf2edc'),(1628,28,'listing',''),(1629,28,'_listing','field_5ad0b7893e02c'),(1630,30,'billboard_logo_text',''),(1631,30,'_billboard_logo_text','field_5ac4d0a0f95d7'),(1632,30,'billboard_logo',''),(1633,30,'_billboard_logo','field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(1634,30,'billboard_heading','Working in project management and delivery'),(1635,30,'_billboard_heading','field_5acb7982f284a'),(1636,30,'billboard_intro_text','Government is in the middle of huge, transformational projects, with more on the horizon. The profile and prestige of project delivery professionals in the public sector has never been higher.'),(1637,30,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5acb79ea29832'),(1638,30,'billboard_image','9'),(1639,30,'_billboard_image','field_5acb79be29831'),(1640,30,'billboard',''),(1641,30,'_billboard','field_5acb795af2849'),(1642,30,'main_content_heading','Making change happen'),(1643,30,'_main_content_heading','field_5ac4d5e562da0'),(1644,30,'main_content_paragraph_1','Project delivery in the Civil Service is about transforming society. Our projects help improve people\'s lives and make government work better. '),(1645,30,'_main_content_paragraph_1','field_5ac4d60162da1'),(1646,30,'main_content_paragraph_2','Our projects are complex, ambitious and huge - really huge. We\'re currently spending around £500 billion on things like, making Tax Digital - the whole system, end-to end, creating an online court system and a digital census ready for 2021.\r\nMake no mistake, when we say you\'ll have the chance to change the UK for the better, we mean it.'),(1647,30,'_main_content_paragraph_2','field_5ac4d65cd4870'),(1648,30,'main_content_image_1','12'),(1649,30,'_main_content_image_1','field_5ac4d6e6993f0'),(1650,30,'main_content_paragraph_3','The Project Delivery profession is there to embed this vital skill, and support everyone involved in planning, supporting and delivering projects. We\'re fairly new, but growing fast. When you join us, you\'ll become part of a thriving community, with networks promoting collaboration, sharing best practices, offering advice and support, and informing strategies.'),(1651,30,'_main_content_paragraph_3','field_5ac4d66bd4871'),(1652,30,'main_content_image_2','12'),(1653,30,'_main_content_image_2','field_5ac4d6f8993f1'),(1654,30,'main_content_paragraph_4','We\'ll help you plan your career path, with guidance and formal mentoring available from colleagues who\'ve seen - and done - it all.\r\nWe offer a dedicated project delivery curriculum which blends work-based, online and classroom learning in line with best practice from top performing public and private sector organisations. And many of our courses come with accredited or validated qualifications.'),(1655,30,'_main_content_paragraph_4','field_5ad0898470360'),(1656,30,'main_content',''),(1657,30,'_main_content','field_5ac4d5c762d9f'),(1658,30,'content_block_vertical_image','12'),(1659,30,'_content_block_vertical_image','field_5ac4d76b70507'),(1660,30,'content_block_vertical_quote','I\'m working on some of the country\'s most pressing security projects on a scale unparalleled in the private sector.'),(1661,30,'_content_block_vertical_quote','field_5ac4d77670508'),(1662,30,'content_block_vertical_forename','Gregg'),(1663,30,'_content_block_vertical_forename','field_5ac4d7d894b09'),(1664,30,'content_block_vertical_surname','Harfleet'),(1665,30,'_content_block_vertical_surname','field_5ac4d7ea94b0a'),(1666,30,'content_block_vertical_role','Civil Service Fast Stream, Ministry of Defence'),(1667,30,'_content_block_vertical_role','field_5ac4d7f794b0b'),(1668,30,'content_block_vertical',''),(1669,30,'_content_block_vertical','field_5ac4d74770506'),(1670,30,'factoid_factoid_0_fact',''),(1671,30,'_factoid_factoid_0_fact','field_5ac4da06ba