moved 41 million employees to the real-time PAYE system: discover what she learned from the process.'),(1739,30,'_sub_repeater_items_2_body','field_5acdc4d6f678d'),(1740,30,'sub_repeater_items_2_image','12'),(1741,30,'_sub_repeater_items_2_image','field_5acdc4f3f678e'),(1742,30,'sub_repeater_items','3'),(1743,30,'_sub_repeater_items','field_5acdc49ef678a'),(1744,30,'sub_repeater',''),(1745,30,'_sub_repeater','field_5acdc481f6789'),(1746,30,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','Make a real difference'),(1747,30,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','field_5ad09fb6a4e80'),(1748,30,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','You\'ll be based in a particular department, but don\'t expect to be there forever. You\'ll be part of a talent pool – called upon to work wherever you can add value.'),(1749,30,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','field_5ad09fd4a4e81'),(1750,30,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','You\'ll also get the chance to work on our cross-department Smarter Working Programmes. They may not sound glamorous, but it\'s how we\'re transforming the entire Civil Service.'),(1751,30,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','field_5ad09ff8a4e82'),(1752,30,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','Big enough for you?'),(1753,30,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','field_5ad0a185f893c'),(1754,30,'sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras',''),(1755,30,'_sub_content_multiple_0_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras','field_5ad0a61054bc4_field_5ad09f94a4e7f'),(1756,30,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','Discipline, flexibility and creativity'),(1757,30,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_heading','field_5ad09fb6a4e80'),(1758,30,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','Whatever your level or experience, you\'ll neeed to have the passion and drive to support the delivery of projects at scale. You’ll need to be adaptable - goals, timescales and even the political environment can change, and you\'ll need the skills and creativity to adapt. '),(1759,30,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_1','field_5ad09fd4a4e81'),(1760,30,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','And beyond your formal skills, you\'ll need to be brilliant at building relationships - with the huge range of people who\'ll make your project a success.'),(1761,30,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_2','field_5ad09ff8a4e82'),(1762,30,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','We\'re Agile, but we\'re flexible and imaginative in how we work : we\'ll expect you to adapt the delivery methodologies to each unique situation. '),(1763,30,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras_paragraph_3','field_5ad0a185f893c'),(1764,30,'sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras',''),(1765,30,'_sub_content_multiple_1_content_area_content_block_with_3_paras','field_5ad0a61054bc4_field_5ad09f94a4e7f'),(1766,30,'sub_content_multiple','2'),(1767,30,'_sub_content_multiple','field_5ad0a5dc54bc3'),(1768,30,'listing_heading','We\'re looking for specialists in:'),(1769,30,'_listing_heading','field_5ad0b7bcf2edb'),(1770,30,'listing_items_0_item','Project Delivery'),(1771,30,'_listing_items_0_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1772,30,'listing_items_1_item','Project Management'),(1773,30,'_listing_items_1_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1774,30,'listing_items_2_item','Business Case, Budget and Resources'),(1775,30,'_listing_items_2_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1776,30,'listing_items_3_item','Stakeholder Management'),(1777,30,'_listing_items_3_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1778,30,'listing_items_4_item','Risk Management'),(1779,30,'_listing_items_4_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1780,30,'listing_items_5_item','Project Performance, Controls and Assurance'),(1781,30,'_listing_items_5_item','field_5ad0b7e2f2edd'),(1782,30,'listing_items','6'),(1783,30,'_listing_items','field_5ad0b7ccf2edc'),(1784,30,'listing',''),(1785,30,'_listing','field_5ad0b7893e02c'),(1786,28,'rpg-team','13'),(1787,31,'_edit_last','1'),(1788,31,'_edit_lock','1525359876:1'),(1789,31,'_wp_page_template','page-layout-b.php'),(1790,31,'billboard_logo_text',''),(1791,31,'_billboard_logo_text','field_5ac4d0a0f95d7'),(1792,31,'billboard_logo',''),(1793,31,'_billboard_logo','field_5ac4d10ed8314'),(1794,31,'billboard_heading','Working in digital data and technology'),(1795,31,'_billboard_heading','field_5acb7982f284a'),(1796,31,'billboard_intro_text','Government is transforming the way it delivers services to the public and business, and digital is at the heart of this revolution.'),(1797,31,'_billboard_intro_text','field_5acb79ea29832'),(1798,31,'billboard_image','11'),(1799,31,'_billboard_image','field_5acb79be29831'),(1800,31,'billboard',''),(1801,31,'_billboard','field_5acb795af2849'),(1802,31,'main_content_heading','Join the revolution'),(1803,31,'_main_content_heading','field_5ac4d5e562da0'),(1804,31,'main_content_paragraph_1','It all started with GOV.UK, which has changed the way government speaks to people – and set new expectations from the public on how they want to access services.'),(1805,31,'_main_content_paragraph_1','field_5ac4d60162da1'),(1806,31,'main_content_paragraph_2','Digital is how we deliver our services, but behind the technology is something far more important – an obsession with users: finding out what they need, and then delivering it to them in the simplest, clearest and fastest way possible. We help all government departments attract, develop and retain the people and skills they need to achieve the transformation they’re looking for.'),(1807,31,'_main_content_paragraph_2','field_5ac4d65cd4870'),(1808,31,'main_content_image_1','12'),(1809,31,'_main_content_image_1','field_5ac4d6e6993f0'),(1810,31,'main_content_paragraph_3','The Digital Data & Technology (DDAT) profession is there to embed digital skills throughout the Civil Service. We’re smart and passionate about our work, and we have big plans. We believe in developing best practice and then sharing it throughout government.'),(1811,31,'_main_content_paragraph_3','field_5ac4d66bd4871'),(1812,31,'main_content_image_2','12'),(1813,31,'_main_content_image_2','field_5ac4d6f8993f1'),(1814,31,'main_content_paragraph_4','You’ll be encouraged to develop your skills: our in-house GDS Academy delivers a huge range of training and development – not just in digital and data, but in project management, UX and user research. And we’re happy for you to try them all - whatever your formal job role.'),(1815,31,'_main_content_paragraph_4','field_5ad0898470360'),(1816,31,'main_content',''),(1817,31,'_main_content','field_5ac4d5c762d9f'),(1818,31,'content_block_vertical_image','12'),(1819,31,'_content_block_vertical_image','field_5ac4d76b70507'),(1820,31,'content_block_vertical_quote','To see that we can build an excellent profession where software developers are valued and leading in their field has really inspired me.'),(1821,31,'_content_block_vertical_quote','field_5ac4d77670508'),(1822,31,'content_block_vertical_forename','Jonny'),(1823,31,'_content_block_vertical_forename','field_5ac4d7d894b09'),(1824,31,'content_block_vertical_surname','Cavell'),(1825,31,'_content_block_vertical_surname','field_5ac4d7ea94b0a'),(1826,31,'content_block_vertical_role','Home Office, Head of Development, DDAT'),(1827,31,'_content_block_vertical_role','field_5ac4d7f794b0b'),(1828,31,'content_block_vertical',''),(1829,31,'_content_block_vertical','field_5ac4d74770506'),(1830,31,'factoid_factoid_0_fact',''),(1831,31,